{"tid":2217193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄧炳強接受葛珮帆「訪問」講修例 寸爆記協 稱黃背心為「任何人記者」斥有人想搶犯","createTime":"2020-09-25T09:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T04:41:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"f593c48a03d43d4a66215fb04a65b8fe07b6794b","tid":2217193,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:13:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/367H9gk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F367H9gk&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=8d914be9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/367H9gk</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）警方修改《警察通例》中傳媒代表定義，記協和攝記協的會員證將不獲「認可」。警務處處長鄧炳強沒有公開回應，只在警察總部接受了民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆的「訪問」。鄧炳強寸爆記協，「我會叫啲黃背心嘅人做『任何人記者』，記協話任何人都係公民記者，我同意！任何人都可以用相機記錄同拍攝，但呢啲我唔能夠確定係咪對我哋會構成危險。」<br />\n<br />\n再轟記者阻礙警方執法<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強斥道，有穿上黃背心的人士在衝突現場進行非採訪工作，包括參與遊行，和刻意阻礙警方工作，「（警方）想捉賊（記者）就擋住我哋、搶犯，攻擊我哋，掟雪糕筒，掟喺路邊。」鄧炳強又稱，記者在以前過往較合作和自律、不會刻意阻礙警方的工作，和不會攻擊和對警方構成危險。"},{"pid":"dde2598ba3bdc2b731290a9b79a810bd18953b01","tid":2217193,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e89902fbbf73812977a4f4496cdc0b1af04cbc","tid":2217193,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12407f06c3f6829031256083424be221488e547b","tid":2217193,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dde2598ba3bdc2b731290a9b79a810bd18953b01","tid":2217193,"ui